Overview
========

szl is a tiny, embeddable scripting engine inspired by Tcl and shell.

For more information, see the user manual at http://www.dimakrasner.com/szl.

Building
========

  $ make
  $ make install

Note: On x86_64 replace the "make" command with

  $ CC="cc -fPIC" make

You will need to run

  $ make clean

first if your attempt to build with

  $ make

failed.

Documentation
=============

To build the user manual:

  $ cd doc; make szl.html

To build the API documentation:

  $ cd doc; make api_docs

